  "original_title": "'\u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd'",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'India's security will be assured'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been declared that Sri Lanka will not allow Sri Lankan soil or maritime territory to be used as a security threat to India.",
        "He mentioned in New Delhi yesterday (31) that India had also given this assurance to Sri Lanka in 1987.",
        "Morakoda described India as a 'logical partner' in Sri Lanka's efforts to overcome its economic crisis.",
        "Since the beginning of this year, India has provided aid worth $3.8 billion to Sri Lanka.",
        "However, Moragoda also mentioned that the difficult times for Sri Lanka are not over yet. (a)"
      ],
